      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-icon"><i class="ph ph-puzzle-piece"></i></div>
      <div class="step-text">
        <strong>Identify Your Missing Category</strong>
        Within your sphere, think about what classification would make your group stronger. Even if they never join the chapter &mdash; knowing that connection exists is valuable. That event planner you know? They belong in someone's referral stream.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-icon"><i class="ph ph-arrows-left-right"></i></div>
      <div class="step-text">
        <strong>Make the Introduction Anyway</strong>
